The paper deals with the problem of distributed state estimation over a time-varying communication graph, which involves concepts from control theory, information theory, and network science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and optimization, which suggests categories such as cs.MA (Machine Learning) and cs.LG (Learning).
